<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.9.4">
<l>mikkāṉai maṟaiyāy virintaviḷak kaiyeṉṉuḷ</l>
<l>pukkāṉaip pukaḻcēr polikiṉṟapoṉ malaiyai</l>
<l>takkāṉaik kaṭikait taṭaṅkuṉṟiṉ micaiyirunta</l>
<l>vakkārak kaṉiyai yaṭaintuyn tupōṉēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking refuge in the exalted one, the lamp that illuminates as the Vedas,</l>
<l>The one who entered my heart, the golden mountain</l>
<l>Which is celebrated with praise, the virtuous one, the sweet fruit</l>
<l>Which sits atop broad Kaṭikai mountain, I was finally saved.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
